subject: United States Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: On the Open’s second Monday, Mardy Fish, the No. 8 seed, got caught in a maelstrom of Jo-Wilfried Tsonga’s power and nature’s bluster, losing 6-4, 6-7 (5), 3-6, 6-4, 6-2.
